A CANSA Shavathon and blood drive will be held at Riverside Mall tomorrow, February 25, at 10:00. The drive is being supported by Emnotweni, Riverside Mall, Lowvelder, Radio Laeveld, RISE fm and the Riverside Park Precint Association. Attendees are asked to remember their masks, and to sanitise their hands and maintain a safe distance from others during the drive. All are welcome to join and support the event by shaving, cutting or colouring their hair for CANSA as well as to donate blood. The event will end at 15:00. ALSO READ: Our City of Mbombela initiative aims to keep the municipality safe, clean.